Index >  IfFeederLoaded

IfFeederLoaded

Description

Returns whether or not there are documents loaded in the Data Source's feeder when IfFeederEnabled and IfPaperDetectable are true. This is a read-only property.

Data type

bool

Default value

true

Syntax

.IfFeederLoaded;

Remarks

Set this property after OpenSource() and before AcquireImage().

Make sure IfFeederEnabled is true before use this property.

When an error occurs, check ErrorCode or ErrorString for error information.

See also

IfAutoFeed
IfFeederEnabled
